<p>Applicants wishing to commence studies in September 2020 or January 2021 will soon be able to apply via the <a href="https://www.courses.knect365-learning.com/event/covert-investigation-distance-learning-training-course/booking/form/12326" target="_blank">Informa Connect application system</a>.</p>
